    Scenario

Package org.javaToAvalla.model Description

Provides the classes and interfaces for managing scenarios and terms in the Avalla framework.

The model package contains the core class Scenario, which represents a sequence of AvallaTerm objects, managing the flow and validity of scenarios.

The terms sub-package contains the specific types of terms, including JavaTerm and AvallaTerm.
